Subpart A_General Provisions and Administration 


 268.101 

Authority, purpose and scope. 


(a) 

Authority. 

The regulations in this part (12 CFR part 268) are issued by the Board of Governors of the Federal Reserve System under
the authority of sections 10(4) and 11(i), (k) and (l) of the Federal Reserve Act (partially codified in 12 U.S.C. 244
and 248(i), (k) and (l)).

