(11) If the local redevelopment authority does not express in writing its interest in a specific property during the
allotted 1-year period, the disposal agency shall again notify HUD of the date of availability of the property for
homeless assistance. HUD may then list the property in the 

Federal Register 

as suitable and available after the base closes following the previous McKinney Act procedures.

(12) The listing of base closure property from the 1991 and subsequent rounds of base closures reported to HUD shall
