It is important that nozzles used in the design and testing of ORVR-equipped vehicles be similar to those found in use.
Should this committee reach consensus on fuel nozzle geometry specifications, EPA will use a nozzle meeting this
standard in all refueling emissions compliance testing, if the nozzle manufacturers agree to adopt these specifications
