3. Fuel Economy 



This action does not have any direct impact on fuel economy labeling, Corporate Average Fuel Economy (CAFE), or gas
guzzler data submission requirements. Because the changes to the test procedure promulgated in this action may affect
fuel economy measurements,

1

 EPA will not require use of the new procedure for fuel economy testing. Therefore, to generate city fuel economy values,
