Clip-on side shields meet all the Z-87 performance standards that the permanent side shields meet and can be
worn when necessary. To be able to wear proper protection where appropriate and be realistic in its use, will make the
employee not look to side step it and, therefore, make it more effective and safer. If a blanket mandatory permanent
side shield regulation to cover all industrial environments is implemented, it will reverse all gains made in recent
years and will not accomplish its goal for a safer industrial environment. 



OSHA agrees that side protection need not be permanent and that detachable side shields should be permitted as long
