The existing system of easily identifying the manufacturers of the components of eye PPE is embedded in the standard
to assure accountability and is accepted throughout the industry. It should be retained.


 
In addition, a commenter from Monsanto (Ex. 3: 102, pg. 3) stated: 



Since employees are permitted to provide their own eye protection and employers are held accountable to ensure that
employees are wearing the proper eye protection, these markings provide employers a ready way of checking for whether
