Also, a commenter from the Washington State Department of Transportation (Ex. 7: 33) stated: 



I think that additional language regarding skin and hand protection needs to be added to this section so this type of
PPE is not excluded from the selection process. 
 



That commenter also submitted suggested language to address 
hand hazards, and the selection and fit of gloves. 
Boeing (Ex. 7: 38, pg. 2) commented: 



Boeing supports the position that additional guidelines related to body and hand protection are necessary in 1910.132.
Such guidelines should provide information on the selection of hand and body PPE based on reported experience and
